## Agent State Machine

```
                    spawn
  [offline] ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚Üí [online-idle]
      ‚Üë                        ‚îÇ    ‚Üë
      ‚îÇ stop/crash             ‚îÇ    ‚îÇ agent_end event
      ‚îÇ                        ‚îÇ    ‚îÇ
      ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ [online-working]
                               ‚îÇ    ‚Üë
                               ‚îÇ    ‚îÇ prompt delivered
                               ‚Üì    ‚îÇ
                          [online-idle]
```

### States
- `offline` ‚Äî not spawned, or disposed
- `online-idle` ‚Äî session exists, not streaming, ready for messages
- `online-working` ‚Äî session is streaming (isStreaming=true)
- `online-blocked` ‚Äî future: waiting for human input (questionnaire tool)

### Transitions (all logged)
```typescript
interface StateTransition {
  agent: string;
  from: AgentState;
  to: AgentState;
  timestamp: number;
  reason: string;  // "spawned", "prompt_delivered", "turn_complete", "stopped", "crashed", "context_cutoff"
}
```

### Health Monitoring (per agent)
- `lastActivity` ‚Äî timestamp of last event
- `lastTokenTime` ‚Äî timestamp of last text_delta
- `turnStartTime` ‚Äî when current turn started
- Stuck detection: `online-working` for > N seconds with no tokens ‚Üí flag

### Status Snapshot (queryable)
```typescript
interface AgentSnapshot {
  name: string;
  state: AgentState;
  contextPercent: number;
  tokenUsage: { input: number; output: number; total: number };
  cost: number;
  messageStats: { sent: number; received: number; queued: number };
  threadCount: number;
  uptime: number;
  lastActivity: number;
  health: "healthy" | "slow" | "stuck" | "error";
}
```

## Audit Trail / Trace Design

### Single append-only JSONL log: `{agentsDir}/trace.jsonl`

Every event gets a line:
```typescript
type TraceEntry =
  | { type: "message"; message: Message }
  | { type: "state_change"; transition: StateTransition }
  | { type: "agent_spawn"; name: string; config: AgentConfig; timestamp: number }
  | { type: "agent_stop"; name: string; reason: string; timestamp: number }
  | { type: "tool_call"; agent: string; tool: string; params: any; timestamp: number }
  | { type: "delivery"; messageId: string; status: "delivered" | "read" | "failed"; timestamp: number }
  | { type: "thread_created"; threadId: string; participants: string[]; timestamp: number }
  | { type: "thread_exhausted"; threadId: string; count: number; timestamp: number }
  | { type: "service_start"; timestamp: number }
  | { type: "service_stop"; timestamp: number }
  | { type: "client_connect"; clientType: string; timestamp: number }
  | { type: "client_disconnect"; clientType: string; timestamp: number }
  | { type: "error"; agent?: string; error: string; timestamp: number }
```

### Properties
- **Append-only** ‚Äî never modified, only appended
- **ALL messages traced** ‚Äî including `online-only` that weren't delivered
- **Replayable** ‚Äî service can rebuild state from trace on restart
- **Queryable** ‚Äî tools can filter by agent, thread, time range, type
- **Rotatable** ‚Äî future: rotate when file exceeds N MB

